list.name: Default
list.comment: Implemented the CalendarNotes as a 'grouped' option, supporting both old and new but not at the same time; use a checked menu item as a toggle.

task.summary: Default task
No SCR; Fixed event sorting to happen every time (other than for an archive), not just after aging.
No SCR; Resolved a case-sensitive regression issue with acquiring GroupInfo from File.
No SCR; Added handling for null 'Found In', which hopefully does not happen now, after the previous check-in.
No SCR; Added handling for null 'Found In.groupType'.
No SCR; Added a new toolkit feature: Show Keepers, and used it to remove deleted groups from their keepers.
No SCR; fine-tuning.
SCR00123 - Changes in empty branch handling.
SCR00123 - Fine tuning the solution before adding tests.
SCR00123 - Added tests, refined the solution. Repaired the older SearchTest.
SCR00123 - Added a new test class (before; checking it in now).
No SCR; added a new test class for the ArchiveTreePanel.
No SCR; checking in txt files, pre development pause.
No SCR; trivial cleanups prior to going dormant.
Text file updates
Upgraded Java from 8 to 16.
update to the DEVELOP.LOG
Changes from Java upgrade; different right mouse button handling.
Adding a Log capability to NoteGroups, initial cut, mixed with fixes & adjustments for several other classes.
Adding a Log capability to NoteGroups, initial cut.
New LogGroupPanel, and Goals now a JTabbedPane view with Milestones and Log. Still initial cut.
Added paging to LogGroupPanel and GoalGroupPanel, and new logic added to handle tabs changing.
A change to a log entry now enables the Goal Save menu item.
Tied the Undo capability for Goal to its Log, with an overridden updateGroup method.
Goal Panel now a grouping of 3 panels, no notes of its own but still has properties.
Finalized the 3 panels for Goals, split its data file between properties and milestones, fixed Save As.
Starting a new TodoNoteGroup with a full GroupInfo now, so that the one made by a GoalGroupPanel will have the right GroupType.
From the TreeBranchEditor, disabled (no longer visible) the control to do a Delete of a NoteGroupPanel.
Added the archiveName to the Goal subPanels.
Added the archiveName to the Goal subPanels.
Moved SaveAs and Rename operations under the NoteGroupFile data accessor class, since they are purely file-based. Also moved the static checkFilename method out of BranchHelper.
Changed pre-existing file checks to use NoteGroupDataAccessor methods.
The addNewGroup method is now wired thru a data accessor, for the name check.

Removed the AppIcon class, replacing it with ImageIcon and added DataAccessor methods and wiring to avoid many (but not all) direct-to-file operations. Repaired the rename operation for a Goal's subpanels.
Fixed the 'no time' DayNoteData time setting; can no longer be null.
Fixed event aging with the day being added to is currently open with unsaved changes.
Some fixes and changes - see the DEVELOP.LOG

Pulled the setting of the data accessor out of setUserDataHome as part of the move of file-based operations out from disparate classes and under the DataAccessor umbrella. This affected many test files as well.

Renamed logHome to mbHome (lots of changes, for that). Moved file-based Subjects loads and saves into the FileDataAccessor. Fixed Subject saving for UpcomingEvents and added a clause to the node change handler in AppTreePanel, to invoke the subjects save if there had been a change. This fixed a problem where a subject could be added while in one NoteGroup but did not show up in a different NoteGroup of the same type, when changing tree nodes.

Removed Merge for UpcomingEvents, removed direct File statements from the TodoList merge and from the BranchHelper. Moved the getGroupNames interface method from the NoteGroupDataAccessor to the DataAccessor, moved the implementation from NoteGroupFile to FileDataAccessor.
Work on moving AppUtil methods to DataAccessors. Removed the inner class NoteIcon from the IconNoteComponent. Some initial work towards converting iconFileString over to an IconInfo.
Fixed .ico icons, genericized icon selection, refinements to getImageIcon methods, now in two places to support either NoteGroups or MB app needs.
Removed DayNoteDefaults and EventNoteDefaults, after moving their data members into the AppOptions.
Finished dereferencing the Milestone icons. There are now no improper instances of the separator char or of a File constructor.

Test changes, mostly due to AppTreePanel interactions. One fail remains - the Todo item focus test, because of unexplained Notifier methods somehow not being Overridden. Commit now, to get back to this point in case fixing it makes things worse.

Misc fixes for new IJ complaints about possible nulls, and a number of rawtypes and unchecked warnings to be cleared. As for the todo item focus issue, it came down to the NoteGroupPanel having its own Notifier, and tests were of course not replacing that one. Now it takes the one from the AppTreePanel, if the instance is not null.
Remaining test remediations needed to get class coverage back up to 100%.
Start of a tabbed approach to CalendarNoteGroups
Consolidated branch editor code in advance of adding the tabbed calendar note group. Also some alpha-reordering of other methods; check-in needed to clear the noise prior to new work.
Implemented the CalendarNotes as a 'grouped' option, supporting both old and new but not at the same time; use a checked menu item as a toggle.
